title: Deep Learning with Keras and Tensorflow
about: Build and train deep learning models using Keras and TensorFlow. Topics include CNNs, RNNs, and advanced model architectures.

topics.name: Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs)
topics.details: Image processing and feature extraction using CNNs.

topics.name: Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs)
topics.details: Sequence modeling and time series analysis with RNNs.

topics.name: Advanced Architectures
topics.details: Explore deeper and more complex neural network structures.

summary: This module focuses on building and training advanced deep learning models using Keras and TensorFlow, including both CNNs and RNNs.
